msgid "DISCLAIMER"
msgstr "免责声明"

#. DISCLAIMER_PART_1
msgid "MOTHER: Encore is a free, unofficial fan reimagining of MOTHER 1 and is not affiliated with Nintendo or Shigesato Itoi. This game offers a uniquely different experience from the original and should not be seen as a replacement for it."
msgstr "《地球冒险：加演》是《地球冒险：开端/MOTHER 1》的\\n非官方免费粉丝重构版本，与任天堂或糸井重里无关。\\n本作提供了与原作截然不同的独特体验，\\n不应被视作原作的代替品。"

#. DISCLAIMER_PART_2
msgid "We recommend supporting the MOTHER series by playing the games via official releases or by purchasing official merchandise."
msgstr "我们建议通过游玩官方发行版本\\n或购买官方周边商品来支持\\n《地球冒险/MOTHER》系列。"

